Package org.blockchain_innovation.factom.client.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FactomdClient
    This is the factomd client that allows you to access all Rpc Methods of factomd
    FactomRequest
    A composition class around the RpcRequest to make the request and response structure symmetric and easily extendable.
    FactomResponse<Result>
    A composition class around the RpcResponse to get access to different values from a server response, like http codes, errors, results.
    LowLevelClient
    The lowlevel client allows you to do direct exchanges (request, responses).
    WalletdClient
    This is the walletd client that allows you to access all Rpc Methods of walletd
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddressKeyConversions
    Address Conversions class to help with extracting keys from addresses or creating an address from a key.
